## Limitations

The study is context-specific, focusing on a Chinese company, which may limit the generalizability of the findings to other cultural or organizational settings. Additionally, the research does not explore long-term impacts of remote work on career development or organizational dynamics. Further studies could provide a broader understanding of remote work's implications across different industries and regions.